## 0. Definitions

- **Work**: the `cta-v1` skill, including all source files, references,
  templates, configuration, and documentation distributed under this
  license.
- **Original Creator**: Anja Evermoor. Holds all rights not explicitly
  granted herein.
- **Licensee**: any party other than the Original Creator who receives,
  uses, distributes, or modifies the Work.
- **Adaptation**: any derivative work, modification, port, integration,
  embedding, or substantive reuse of the Work or any portion thereof.
- **Small Entity**: any organization or individual with both (a) headcount
  of nineteen (19) or fewer persons and (b) annual gross revenue of two
  hundred forty-seven thousand eight hundred twenty-nine US dollars
  (USD $247,829) or less.
- **Attribution Manifest**: the `ATTRIBUTION.json` file accompanying the
  Work, declaring authorship, license, frameworks, and the provenance seal.
- **Provenance Seal**: the SHAKE256-512-bit composite hash of the Work
  derived via the Epoch Rule30 Salt Stream construction (see
  `scripts/provenance_seal.sh`) and stored in `provenance.json`.

